<h2 id="who-its-for">🎯 Who Trainerize Is For</h2>

**Perfect fit:**
- Solo personal trainers building an online coaching business alongside in-person sessions
- Boutique fitness studios (1-5 locations) adding hybrid training revenue
- Trainers focused on transformation programs with strong habit-coaching components
- Gyms using ABC Fitness or Mindbody as their core management system

**Workable but requires customization:**
- Multi-location franchises (6-20 locations) — budget for reporting integration work
- High-volume online coaching businesses (500+ clients) — workflow automation becomes essential
- Nutrition-focused coaches — supplement with dedicated meal planning tools

**Look elsewhere:**
- Enterprise gym chains (50+ locations) seeking unified analytics without custom development
- Coaches whose primary delivery is live video sessions (Zoom-native platforms serve better)
- Operators wanting all-in-one business management including front desk and member management

