<h2 id="integrations">🔗 Integration Ecosystem</h2>

Trainerize connects with the tools fitness businesses actually use:

**Gym Management:** Mindbody, ABC Fitness, ClubReady, Pike13
**Wearables:** Apple Health, Google Fit, Fitbit, Garmin, Whoop, MyZone
**Nutrition:** MyFitnessPal
**Payments:** Stripe (native), PayPal
**Automation:** Zapier (enables hundreds of secondary connections)
**Scheduling:** Calendly, Acuity, native booking

The Zapier connection is particularly powerful. We've built automations that trigger onboarding sequences when clients sign up, alert trainers when client engagement drops, and sync client data to CRM platforms. If you're not leveraging Zapier with Trainerize, you're leaving efficiency on the table.

